g":"買過一次垃圾到暈<br />\n再平都唔會再買<br />\n好撚難食"},{"pid":"3883490d78138f21570d8b88ba4d1bc570e73fc3","tid":767835,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"買手代理咪又係屠房高層搞出黎<br />\n<br />\n話係黑社會 根本自己最黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e78c1702cc8790680c8e2df6e2a24849e782dae","tid":767835,"uid":193913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d404be37f137074c29ec812eafeda7e0739fd7f","tid":767835,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a56c6a2585913bf1a4efeea1c00e1a09f59f4fb","tid":767835,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bab74426e6fbd2dcad7380487f8e00804afb52","tid":767835,"uid":35752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"不過未必係內地，馬來西亞、泰國仲平！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那會俾你咁做?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"因為要打爛支那人飯碗，所以俾人淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0af021beb68bf50adc96c09015e27a77ce39f1","tid":767835,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"迫人買豬咁撚仆街<br />\n<br />\n仲有王法嘅"}]}